---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About · ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="About CBicycle. · 关于 CBicycle。" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="prose-wrap">
			<div class="post-head">
				<h1>About 关于</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="prose">
				<p>
					CBicycle is a small personal site about cycling — the rides, the notes scribbled
					afterwards, and the tools that make the next ride a little better.
				</p>
				<p>
					CBicycle 是一个关于骑行的小小个人站点 —— 记录骑过的路线、事后随手写下的笔记,以及那些让下一次骑行更好的小工具。
				</p>
				<p>
					It runs on <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a> and
					<a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com/">Cloudflare Pages</a>, and it's quietly a work in
					progress. 本站用 Astro + Cloudflare Pages 搭建,还在慢慢长大。
				</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.post-head h1 {
		margin: 0;
	}
	.prose :global(p) {
		margin-bottom: 1.2em;
	}
</style>
